body.description: Diono Radian 3R, 3-in-1 Convertible Car Seat, Rear Facing & Forward Facing, 10 Years 1 Car Seat, Slim Fit 3 Across, Jet BlackThe Diono Radian 3R is the original slim-fit 3 across All-in-One convertible car seat, designed to protect from baby to booster seat (5 - 120 lb / 2.2 - 54 kg). Lovingly engineered with the famous Diono steel reinforced frame and now rear facing for even longer, expect 10 years of safety from just one car seat. Designed and engineered with complete rear facing protection, so you can keep them in a safe rear facing convertible car seat for longer up to 50 pounds. Built with a mechanically engineered, reinforced steel frame, made from automotive grade high strength steel, the radian is always ready to shield and protect. And when your family grows, the slim-fit design will fit 3 across in most vehicles without compromising child safety or passenger comfort. Our SuperLATCH system (UAS Compatible) makes installation easy and super secure. As travel car seat experts, Diono have naturally built in super portable and convenient features to the Radian 3R with original fold for easy transport and storage and easy remove machine washable covers. The radian is also aircraft certified (FAA approved), so you can take safety with you wherever you go.Diono Car Seat Cup Holders for Radian, Everett and Rainier Car Seats, Pack of 2 Cup Holders, Blue SkyThe Diono Cup Holder 2 Pack is a clever solution to accommodate all of their home comfort on the move. The deep angled sides keep cups and toys securely in place with simple click and a twist installation. The handy 2 pack of Cup Holders are compatible with all Diono All-in-One convertible car seats and the Everett NXT booster too with all seats featuring 2 spaces for the cup holders to fit.
